\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Many old notebooks and letters are, however, in my possession which have helped me; but my two latest surviving sisters, whose minds were sure storehouses of family events, and to whom I always referred whenever I wanted a date or particulars of a long-past fact, are now both dead, the one at the\~}{\f0\fs24\b0 [}{\f0\fs24\b0 2]age of ninety-three and the other at ninety-seven, each with a clear and vigorous mind to nearly the very end of her life. I have hardly any contemporary friends left who could aid in recalling the circumstances of my childhood and boyhood. With rare exceptions, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93All, all are gone, the old familiar faces.\u8221\'94}{ }}